name: Trystana
overview:
Trystana (pronounced /trÉªstana/) is an online dating site where people can meet singles living nearby.

Trystana also integrates with social networking sites like Facebook to bring people together on their favorite social networks.

Trystana is owned and operated by Trystana Social Media Inc., a privately held media company headquartered in Richmond Hill, Ontario, Canada. Trystana Social Media Inc.’s mission is to conduct research on social networking phenomena and provide innovative, high-tech and internet-based solutions to connect people based on their demographics and interests.
